Source: online-advisor
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/knizhnik/online_advisor

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-online-advisor
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-online-advisor
Depends: ${postgresql:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Suggest missing indexes and statistics online for PostgreSQL PGVERSION
 online_advisor instruments query execution and reports candidate indexes,
 extended statistics, and statements that may benefit from being prepared.
